    <line>while my right hand grasped a pistol which</line>
    <line>was hidden in my bosom; every sound terrified</line>
    <line>me but I <del rend="strikethrough">s</del> resolved that I would sell my life</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">as</del> dearly <del rend="strikethrough">as possible</del> and
      not relax the impending</line>
    <line>conflict untill my own life, or that of my adversa</line>
