    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line rend="indent2">Elizabeth observed my agitation for some</line>
    <line>time in timid and fearful silence; at length she</line>
    <line>said, What is it that agitates you<del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>r</unclear></del>, my
      dear Victor?</line>
    <line>What is it you fear?</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
    <line rend="indent2">Oh! peace, peace, my love, replied I, this night</line>
    <line>and all will be safe; but this night is dreadful,</line>
    <line><unclear>&#x2014;</unclear>very dreadful.</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
